<section id="abstract">
    <p>This document provides a mapping from [[[ODRL-VOCAB]]] concepts to DPV concepts to assist implementations using both of them together. Currently, this activity is a work in progress and the DPVCG welcomes contributions and participations for it.</p>
</section>
    {{ sotd('mappings-odrl') }}
