<section id="introduction">
  <h2>Introduction</h2>
  <p>Concepts in DPV are aligned with those from [[[ODRL-VOCAB]]] by using [[SKOS]] relations. In addition, to enable the use of DPV in ODRL policies, certain relations are expressed as instances of ODRL's Operand concepts. This mapping is also provided in <a href="dpv-odrl.ttl">RDF</a> and <a href="dpv-odrl.csv">CSV</a> form for convenience. This mapping will assist the [[[GUIDE-ODRL]]].</p>
  <p>The DPVCG aims to create and provide a profile containing DPV concepts to enable the use of all DPV vocabularies in adherence with ODRL recommendations, and welcomes contributions and participations in this process.</p>
